  {
    "hotel_id": "926594",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/the-blossom-resort-danang_4/hotel/da-nang-vn.html",
    "name": "The Blossom Resort Island Da Nang - Onsen Included",
    "detail": "I loved loved loved the resort and wish I could have stayed longer. My partner and I were only there for one night - and not even the full night because we left for the airport at 3am. I had already been staying in Hoi An and as I saw that they have a shuttle to Hoi An, I messaged the hotel and they kindly reserved a spot on the shuttle for me so my partner and I could get from Hoi An to the resort in Da Nang easily. Check in process was easy and smooth. Our bags were taken care of and we were given a 30 minute massage coupon + pho coupon for dinner. We ended up upgrading our massages to a full body 1 hour message and it was very relaxing. There's also an onsen but I didn't get to try that since I spent hours by the pool. They have comfy cabanas along the pool and it was never too too crowded. We ordered food to enjoy by the pool as well. It was beautiful watching the night sky take over and the Ferris wheel lighting up. The room itself was lovely and clean. AC worked amazing. They also had welcome fruit for us in the room :). Dinner is in the restaurant. The pho coupon allows you to have bottomless pho :) delicious! The staff were also very friendly and gentle. They always had a big smile on their face and made our experience at the resort a very pleasant one. :)",
