  {
    "hotel_id": "1603126",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/risemount-resort-danang/hotel/da-nang-vn.html",
    "name": "Risemount Premier Resort Danang",
    "detail": "It was lucky to stay in hotel during Vietnam public holiday as reasonable price. The hotel treats me full-board meal included, i was not expected the situation. Also, the staffs are very helpful to introduce us about hotel facility, Da-nang festival and restaurant nearby hotel. During staying, I got exorbitant demands from reception at 12am. the staff came to our room, and press the chime bell. the staff's demand was we need to be quiet. At that moment, we just talked on the bed and playing soothing music through phone. In the morning, I realized there was not soundproof facility in the room by room. Because I could hear formal conversation next room. Except then, there was awesome experience to stay in hotel. 체크인 할때의 경험도 상당히 좋았으며 방의 크기도 다른 베트남 호텥보다 훨씬 큰 편에 속했습니다. 또한 호텔안에서의 점심, 저녁 식사도 상당히 깔끔했으며 레스토랑에서 먹는 음식을 대접받는 느낌이었습니다. 조식이 나쁘다는 평이 많은데 생각보다 나쁘지 않습니다. 다만, 소음에 예민하신분은 방을 선택하실 때 고려하셔야할 듯합니다. 방의 층고가 높다보니 옆 방의 대화가 얼핏 들릴 수가 있습니다. 그 것만 빼면 숙박 자체는 아주 좋은 경험이었습니다.",
